es-stagehand-ui-label-explanation = [bold]Stagehands[/bold] are a special [italic]out-of-character[/italic] role.
    Instead of playing as a job or character in the round, you [italic]can spectate and influence the crew from beyond the veil[/italic].

    Stagehands can fly around the station and observe the actions, masks, and objectives of all players in the round.
    They can also initiate a variety of votes to mess with players & affect the round.

    {""}[color=red][bold]Warning:[/bold] Once you become a stagehand, you will be [bold]unable to return[/bold] to the theater for the remainder of the round![/color]